    "en": {
      "name": "Six Strike - Double Assault",
      "effect": "Apply 1 of these effects, or if you control 2 or more \"Six Samurai\" monsters, you can apply both, in sequence.\n\u25cf Special Summon 1 \"Six Samurai\" monster with 2000 or less ATK from your hand or GY.\n\u25cf Change 1 monster your opponent controls with 2000 or less ATK to face-down Defense Position.\nDuring your Main Phase: You can banish this card from your GY, then target 1 \"Six Samurai\" monster in your GY; add it to your hand. You can only use 1 \"Six Strike - Double Assault\" effect per turn, and only once that turn.",
      "official": false
    },
